{"tid":928244,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"又葡萄！C朗失獎家姐代抱不平","createTime":"2018-12-04T16:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T08:48:31.000Z","uid":20634,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e87ae445d0ff4f1f52c9fd52a6e6e76b43bb7ef","tid":928244,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/6/256/23818374256/23818166293_600x391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F6%2F256%2F23818374256%2F23818166293_600x391.jpg&h=7b6270dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=qmBz6ZN77ZI7cUQ0dYhunp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=81e7fe68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】早前基斯坦奴朗拿度失落歐洲足協最佳球員，他的二家姐Katia已在instagram上發功替細佬不值，周一C朗又失落金球獎，Katia就聯同大家姐Elma齊齊發聲。<br />\n<br />\n「很無奈，現在這個世界就是這樣，是如此的腐敗，充斥黑手黨與他X的金錢。但上帝的力量能戰勝這一切腐敗。<span style=\"color: red;\">若然未報，只因為時辰未到。</span>」大家姐Elma在instagram上說，連上帝與黑手黨都牽扯進來，實在令人摸不著頭腦。<br />\n<br />\nKatia跟大家姐一樣，甫上基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）過去得獎的威水相，評語就精警得多：「這位就是世界上最佳球員&mdash;&mdash;當然只限於在識波的人眼中。」<br />\n<br />\n對兩姊妹的一唱一和，有網民不以為然：「C朗今年得票第2。你們（兩姊妹）這樣糾纏下去，實在很小家。」今屆金球獎周一揭曉，莫迪歷以大熱姿態奪獎，結束了C朗、美斯的10年壟斷局面。"},{"pid":"ffdcd51fe45fcd4e9a30215117de22b2f49c203c","tid":928244,"uid":90515,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"無摩迪，阿朗都唔會有5金球啦，做人記得飲水思源喎"},{"pid":"10dcc3362057545c5a3fa1217f0bf2641f03006d","tid":928244,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"萄葡牙"},{"pid":"1b40a603aa924224fc3bb43ca661c11d80f86be0","tid":928244,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T08:43:10.000Z","msg":"差老母未出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5362dd0a753f0d6254f037467dae5d1f7bd0a80","tid":928244,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":